{"tid":1840293,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"中央：撤回送中條例","createTime":"2020-01-24T18:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T19:05:51.000Z","uid":331949,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"15d0abe5050ee70902f4ea046cebf9f7235cb654","tid":1840293,"uid":331949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:54:40.000Z","msg":"中央：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vEhOSy3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvEhOSy3.gif&h=e0ec045f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08766475d3b5b68901bf149587a51c4a822d4d60","tid":1840293,"uid":318928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:55:14.000Z","msg":"要快！必須要有612咁大型  已經冇退路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1840260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1840260</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4a2a0844da9839cd5b25b41ad05564776a154682","tid":1840293,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:55:45.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"ab5794c90efe1c2d4ae98db5e6d43b08a0e5c44d","tid":1840293,"uid":331949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a2a0844da9839cd5b25b41ad05564776a154682","tid":1840293,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:55:45.000Z","msg":"On9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:57:50.000Z","msg":"你班廢青黑醫，工都唔敢罷，以為我真係搞你唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c51a9dda1a2d1073fc1cc098a7e6b93710cbfe6","tid":1840293,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3049caacd1b05cbb4ead595bb44dcbb2ad9d71d0","tid":1840293,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:01:51.000Z","msg":"分分鐘<br />\nXi 憎撚到林鄭死<br />\n就係佢呢半年 中國 臉，錢未比佢丟清光<br />\n又肺炎又香港 一定煩到頭都爆<br />\n我係習大 一定殺撚左林鄭先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後搵班黑警制旗，可以調動香港資金返中國 醫病<br />\n如果唔係 中國一定支爆<br />\n呢加其他國家似係食緊花生睇中國呢個病 <br />\n幾時搞到成個中國玩完 再幫佢執屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69c19cd1e2fcb84cf4888dca47d141a21d6066d","tid":1840293,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T19:05:51.000Z","msg":"致四大醫護專業工會<br />\n<br />\n近日致命武漢肺炎肆虐全球，世界各地的政府均已實行嚴謹的防疫措施。唯獨香港特區政府對關口的防疫工作置之不理，令大量懷疑感染新型冠狀病毒的外來患者湧入香港。<br />\n<br />\n港府在防疫工作上力度不足，以及後知後覺的態度，直接令醫護界工作壓力及感染機會大增，甚至需要以抽生死籤來決定進入隔離病房的醫護名單。在未有任何確切治療的方案下，此致命的疫症絕大機會令2003 年沙士事件中，醫護人員因受感染而死亡的傷痛事件重現，再次勾起港人的悲痛回憶。<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，一眾熱心的市民已於2020年1月24日零晨，在《香港地投票》應用程式內發起了一項投票事項。投票只開放予香港境內市民，亦以一系列的措施盡力達至一人一票，其內容如下：<br />\n<br />\n議題：支唔支持醫護大罷工<br />\n投票開放時間：一個月<br />\n截至2020年1月25日零晨為止，24小時內已有1117名香港市民投票，當中約97%支持香港醫護人員罷工，約2%反對及2張廢票。<br />\n<br />\n《香港地投票》應用程式作為一個投票平台，致力為不同民生或政制議題及各種工業行動提供民意基礎。現來信各醫護工會團體，藉此轉達市民的意見。考慮到醫護人員有其專業，亦關乎病人及其家屬的權益。醫護人員罷工與否的決定將完全留待醫護界自行決定，此函只供各大機構作民意參考之用。<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票<br />\n謹啟<br />\n2020-01-25<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org%2FLetter%2F20200125.pdf&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT6nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=c87a0ee0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n有勞大家幫我forword 俾醫護工會同各醫護知<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"}]}